Package com.javatoavalla.avallascenario.impl Description

This package contains implementations of the interfaces defined in the avallaScenario package.

The ScenarioListMapper class implements the ScenarioListMapper interface, providing functionality to convert a list of Scenario objects into a list of ScenarioFile objects.

The ScenarioWriter class implements the ScenarioWriter interface, providing the ability to write a Scenario into a ScenarioFile.
